msgstr "預約到館待提取"

#: ../../source/circulation.rst:1030
msgid "This report will show you all of the items that have holds on them that are available at the library for pulling. If the items are available at multiple branches then all branches with that item available will see the hold to pull until one library triggers the hold."
msgstr "此報表顯示所有圖書館可滿足的預約。若多個圖書館有該預約館藏，則全部顯示，直到其中一個圖書館啟動滿足預約流程。"

